title: [Reim Fortress, Supply Room]
[Reim Fortress, Supply Closet]
description: Piled along each wall are massive slatted wooden crates with the words, "Reim Fortress" burned into the sides.  Faint glimmers from metal objects within hint at their contents, but the large boxes show no obvious point of entry.
